social_posts.post_text: Happy birthday Sunday. uncle clay loves ya💗

as many of you may know I’ve been making music since 2016 
it started off as something I’d do for fun/ just a side hobby. I started taking it serious when I turned 20. Experimenting with different genres and trying new sounds.
I never knew how much I’d fall in love with it, but as time has gone by it’s become my passion in life. I held onto a lot of these songs debating to post them or not. But I felt like the time was right.
This is album is very special to me. It’s about just being yourself and letting go. I used to constantly think about what others would think while listening to my music. this album I finally let everything go. I poured my heart and soul into this one☝️ and this is a very special project to me. I’m super excited for y’all to hear it.
so go give it a listen, it’s a freakin vibe
